text: Syed Sagar is an Indian cricketer who generally plays for Jammu and Kashmir in T20s. He is a right-handed batsman. He holds the record for the highest T20 individual score when batting at number 9 or lower (74). == References == Category:Indian cricketers Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Jammu and Kashmir cricketers Category:People from Srinagar
title: Syed Sagar
